    <div class="admin-instructions">
      <h2>📋 How to Add a New Book</h2>
      <ol>
        <li>Find the public domain PDF on <a href="https://archive.org" target="_blank">archive.org</a> or <a href="https://gutenberg.org" target="_blank">gutenberg.org</a></li>
        <li>Add the book to <code>generate_free_pages.py</code> BOOKS list</li>
        <li>Run the script: <code>python generate_free_pages.py</code></li>
        <li>Git push — Netlify deploys automatically</li>
        <li>Share the link in Facebook groups: <code>/free/your-book-slug</code></li>
      </ol>

      <h2>📣 Facebook Post Template</h2>
      <div class="template-box">
        <p><em>"[HOOK sentence about the book].<br/><br/>
        Published in [YEAR]. Still one of the most powerful books on [TOPIC].<br/><br/>
        It's public domain — I'm sharing a free PDF download here:<br/>
